@gateway_url = https://localhost:7100
@jwt_token = your-jwt-token-here

### Test Gateway Health Check
GET {{gateway_url}}/health

### Test Identity Service through Gateway (No Auth Required)
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/identity/auth/test

### Test Cinema Service through Gateway (No Auth Required)
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/cinemas

### Test Movie Service through Gateway (No Auth Required)
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/movies

### Test Booking Service through Gateway (Auth Required)
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Test Payment Service through Gateway (Auth Required)
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Test Seat Availability through Gateway (Auth Required)
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/seat-availability/showtime/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Test Rate Limiting - Send multiple requests quickly
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/movies

### Test Circuit Breaker - This will fail if downstream service is down
GET {{gateway_url}}/gateway/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}